                <mxCell id="45" value="&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); scrollbar-color: rgb(226, 226, 226) rgb(251, 251, 251); font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Pod Disruption Budget (PDB) — Voluntary Disruption Guard&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); scrollbar-color: rgb(226, 226, 226) rgb(251, 251, 251); font-size: 18px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;scrollbar-color: rgb(226, 226, 226) rgb(251, 251, 251); text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;PDB tells the eviction API: &quot;don&#39;t take down more than X of my Pods at a time&quot;. It protects availability during&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); scrollbar-color: rgb(226, 226, 226) rgb(251, 251, 251);&quot;&gt;voluntary&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;disruptions (drain / upgrade / scale-in), not against node failures.&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=14;arcSize=8;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 1;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#f9f7ed;strokeColor=#36393d;" vertex="1" parent="1">
